{"tid":1512534,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［林鄭戰術升級我又升級］應對林鄭緊急令方法，升級制裁對象至港共政權所有爪牙","createTime":"2019-08-28T02:31:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T02:52:08.000Z","uid":1882,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"57adc24ed8f7bc4edc6fc4e83409bbb9d60e1d91","tid":1512534,"uid":1882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T02:31:37.000Z","msg":"推行人權法案第二章<br />\n<br />\n包括所有屈服於共產黨威壓的公司，設立死線讓公司補救，否則將制裁。<br />\n<br />\n制裁行動包括，禁止該公司的母公司，在美國進行集資行動，限制商業活動。<br />\n<br />\n警隊高層至前線，曾經在6月9至今年年尾以輔警，警員，警隊文員，至前線接聽999專員，一概進行制裁。<br />\n<br />\n制裁行動包括，禁止他們的直屬家庭以及子女移民，限制他們可以出國的地點，如日本，等佢哋有錢冇得用。<br />\n<br />\n官員，所有功能組別，超級區議會出賣香港的，一概家人都將會制裁。<br />\n<br />\n制裁行動包括，禁止他們的直屬家庭以及子女移民，限制他們可以出國的地點，如日本，等佢哋有錢冇得用。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f4d6a56164be9a565446d5bba9ff55b96574ef9","tid":1512534,"uid":89145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T02:31:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"845951f59fbaaf065679d2cfe41149fbbb8f498c","tid":1512534,"uid":284522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T02:31:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PWzcvgg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPWzcvgg.jpg&h=187c67d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQ6joMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=bdafb9e3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQ6joMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=d4afec4f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me